description:
//This review is about Green Chile Pies//

I wish I would have read the other reviews before coming here. Upon hearing about the vegetarian pot pie and veggie chile Frito pie, I was so excited! Then I ate the pot pie and it was like eating old people food. So bland, so boring. I wanted to love it, I tried to trick myself into loving it, but it was useless. The Frito pie was okay, and we actually tried the apple pie and that was fine but I left feeling very unsatisfied. 

Also, the wine and beer selection were awful.
